Facebook post, 5 January 2020 - THE COVID PREDICTION (66 days before WHO). Caption: Jo kabhi socha na hoga ase ase events dekhne ko aur sunne ko milege hum sabko. 2020 Worldy events. Utho jaago. Translation: What was never imagined we will all see and hear. Wake up! Image: Physically I am on Earth, Mentally in Galaxies, Spiritually in another Dimension. Aspect: Coded Signals + Warning - most significant advance warning.